            <title>[AMQ-6504] Scheduler store delivers message to early</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-6504</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When calculating the time block to scheduler new Jobs in the store code truncates instead of rounds the time which leads jobs to get run early in many cases.  &lt;/p&gt;</description>
